In a early screenplay drafts written by Alfred Gough , Miles Millar , and David Hayter for New Line Cinema , and pitted Iron Man against his father Howard Stark , who becomes War Machine .
*
Howard Stark appears in the 2007 animated direct - to - video film The Invincible Iron Man , voiced by John McCook .
*
In , Iron Man named a satellite after his father called the Howard Satellite .
*
Howard Stark is shown in the live - action Marvel Cinematic Universe movie series produced by Marvel Studios , portrayed by Dominic Cooper and John Slattery .
* Gerard Sanders portrayed the character in a brief memorial slideshow presentation in the beginning of the 2008 film Iron Man where he is an acquaintance of Obadiah Stane .
*
Slattery first portrayed the character in the 2010 film Iron Man 2 where it is revealed that he is one of S.H.I.E.L.D. 's co - founders .
Having placed a message for Tony Stark in a film reel , Howard gives Tony closure in their strained relationship while providing his son a diorama of the 1974 Stark Expo to perfect the Arc Reactor which he and Anton Vanko started .
* Cooper first portrayed a younger iteration in the 2011 film that aided in the Super Soldier Project and then the Strategic Scientific Reserve .
His contributions include providing Steve Rogers with both a tactical uniform and shield .
After the Hydra battleship that Rogers raided crashed in the ocean , Stark made attempts to find Rogers before his expeditions led to the Tesseract .
* Cooper reprises his role in Marvel One - Shot film Agent Carter , where Peggy Carter helps Stark during S.H.I.E.L.D. 's formation .
*
A still photograph of Cooper appears in the 2014 film .
*
Slattery reprised his role in the 2015 film Ant - Man .
In a flashback in the late-1980s , he witnesses Hank Pym 's resignation from S.H.I.E.L.D. after the discovery of them trying to replicate the Pym Particles without consent .
While objecting to Pym 's actions , Stark felt that Mitchell Carson did deserve Hank 's punch following Mitchell 's inappropriate comment about Janet van Dyne .
* Slattery again reprised the role in the 2016 film .
On December 16 , 1991 , the car crash said to be the cause of the deaths of Howard and Maria Stark was caused by the Winter Soldier while under Hydra 's control , causing the Starks ' car to crash and then killing the Starks after they survived the initial impact .
